You have these packets and then the parents

00:05:07.810 --> 00:05:12.069
just head away. They just leave. And then
eventually all of the squid are born. Most

00:05:12.069 --> 00:05:16.750
of them are food for fish, but some of them
are able to survive. And so that's the r selected

00:05:16.750 --> 00:05:23.030
species. You're putting your life in growth
